\par\pard\plain \tx0\li720\fi360\sa120\ltrch\loch {\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf6 In a private storage room, Sarah briefs Evan for an upcoming fundraiser, exuding a mix of enthusiasm and worry. She urges him to be mindful, especially around her boss, Marcus Chamberlain, who looks like Morgan Freeman. Her instructions, imbued with belief in Evan and anxiety about the night, set the scene for what seems to be a memorable event.<!$Scr_Ps::4><$Scr_Ps::3>}
