\par\pard\plain \tx0\li720\fi14\sa120\sl264\slmult1\ltrch\loch {\f3\fs24\b0\i1\cf9 <$Scr_Cs::6>[ Begin the scene with Evan and Sarah complimenting each other on their appearance. I have provided a clothing description that should be used in this scene at the beginning. ]}
\par\plain {\f3\fs24\b0\i1\cf9 [ After Evan and Sarah exchanged compliments, she grabbed her glass of wine from the bar. ]<!$Scr_Cs::6>}
