\par\pard\plain \tx0\li720\sa120\sl264\slmult1\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24\b1\i0\cf10 <$Scr_Cs::7>Sarah: <!$Scr_Cs::7>}{\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf6 "Come on, Evan. Let's go talk somewhere privately."}
\par\plain {\f3\fs24\b0\i1\cf9 <$Scr_Cs::6>[ Evan followed Sarah to a small storage room located behind the coat check room.  ]}
\par\plain {\f3\fs24\b0\i1\cf9 [ She closed the door behind them. ]<!$Scr_Cs::6>}
\par\plain {\f2\fs24\b1\i0\cf10 <$Scr_Cs::7>Evan: <!$Scr_Cs::7>}{\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf6 "Is this the make-out room?"}
\par\plain {\f3\fs24\b0\i1\cf9 <$Scr_Cs::6>[ He said with the energy of a teenager in love as he leaned in for a kiss. ]}
\par\plain {\f3\fs24\b0\i1\cf9 [ Sarah spoke In a low voice close to a whisper. ]<!$Scr_Cs::6>}
\par\plain {\f2\fs24\b1\i0\cf10 <$Scr_Cs::7>Sarah:<!$Scr_Cs::7>}{\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf6  "Not here. This is my work. We have to keep a professional." }
\par\plain {\f3\fs24\b0\i1\cf9 <$Scr_Cs::6>[ Evan was not bothered at all by Sarah's comment. ]<!$Scr_Cs::6>}
\par\plain {\f2\fs24\b1\i0\cf10 <$Scr_Cs::7>Evan: <!$Scr_Cs::7>}{\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf6 "Why are we whispering? There's no one here."}
\par\plain {\f3\fs24\b0\i1\cf9 <$Scr_Cs::6>[ Sarah laughed before speaking at a normal volume level.]<!$Scr_Cs::6>}
\par\plain {\f2\fs24\b1\i0\cf10 <$Scr_Cs::7>Sarah: <!$Scr_Cs::7>}{\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf6 "I have no idea."}
\par\plain {\f3\fs24\b0\i1\cf9 <$Scr_Cs::6>[ They both laughed. ]<!$Scr_Cs::6>}
\par\plain {\f2\fs24\b1\i0\cf10 <$Scr_Cs::7>Sarah: <!$Scr_Cs::7>}{\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf6 "I brought you back here because I wanted to prep you for the fundraiser. I should've done this earlier, but I just got so busy."}
\par\plain {\f2\fs24\b1\i0\cf10 <$Scr_Cs::7>Evan: <!$Scr_Cs::7>}{\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf6 "Prep away!"}
\par\plain {\f2\fs24\b1\i0\cf10 <$Scr_Cs::7>Sarah: <!$Scr_Cs::7>}{\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf6 "Well, first, tell me how you're feeling. Are you nervous?"}
\par\plain {\f2\fs24\b1\i0\cf10 <$Scr_Cs::7>Evan: <!$Scr_Cs::7>}{\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf6 "I was extremely nervous when I left my apartment. I decided to call Liz on the two-hour drive to Chicago. She reminded me that no matter how wealthy or sophisticated a person is, they still put on the pants one leg at a time. They still sneeze, burp, cough, cry, and laugh. She also told me that, most importantly, rich or poor, the best people prioritize authenticity. If they don't like me for who I am, then I should simply, as Liz calls it, 'exit gracefully.'"  }
\par\plain {\f2\fs24\b1\i0\cf10 <$Scr_Cs::7>Sarah: <!$Scr_Cs::7>}{\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf6 "And that's all it took to calm your nerves?"}
\par\plain {\f3\fs24\b0\i1\cf9 <$Scr_Cs::6>[ Evan, ever the comic. ]<!$Scr_Cs::6>}
\par\plain {\f2\fs24\b1\i0\cf10 <$Scr_Cs::7>Evan: <!$Scr_Cs::7>}{\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf6 "Well, that and a little help from my friend Jack Daniels that your bartender introduced me to." }
\par\plain {\f3\fs24\b0\i1\cf9 <$Scr_Cs::6>[ Sarah and Evan both laughed. Then Sarah got her serious business look on her face. ]<!$Scr_Cs::6>}
\par\plain {\f2\fs24\b1\i0\cf10 <$Scr_Cs::7>Sarah: <!$Scr_Cs::7>}{\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf6 "This fundraising event is for the nonprofit 'Home Is Where the Heart Is.' It was founded by a very wealthy businessman and gentleman named Marcus Chamberlain \endash  think Morgan Freeman's twin brother."}
\par\plain {\f2\fs24\b1\i0\cf10 <$Scr_Cs::7>Evan:<!$Scr_Cs::7>}{\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf6  "Gotcha!"}
\par\plain {\f2\fs24\b1\i0\cf10 <$Scr_Cs::7>Sarah: <!$Scr_Cs::7>}{\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf6 "This is the third event I've organized for him. I like working for him because he's not a jerk and gives me the autonomy to do the job right. He is quite distinguished, so be on your best behavior around him."}
\par\plain {\f3\fs24\b0\i1\cf9 <$Scr_Cs::6>[ Evan repeats the critical components of words to help him remember. ]<!$Scr_Cs::6>}
\par\plain {\f2\fs24\b1\i0\cf10 <$Scr_Cs::7>Evan: <!$Scr_Cs::7>}{\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf6 "Marcus Chamberlain, Home Is Where the Heart Is, best behavior."}
\par\plain {\f2\fs24\b1\i0\cf10 <$Scr_Cs::7>Evan:<!$Scr_Cs::7>}{\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf6  "What will the funds raised tonight be used for?"}
\par\plain {\f2\fs24\b1\i0\cf10 <$Scr_Cs::7>Sarah: <!$Scr_Cs::7>}{\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf6 "Home Is Where the Heart Is provides funds and volunteers to help low-income families rehab homes in disrepair. They also help rebuild uninsured or underinsured homes lost due to fire or natural disaster."}
\par\plain {\f2\fs24\b1\i0\cf10 <$Scr_Cs::7>Evan: <!$Scr_Cs::7>}{\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf6 "Wow! Those are good causes."}
\par\plain {\f2\fs24\b1\i0\cf10 <$Scr_Cs::7>Sarah<!$Scr_Cs::7>}{\f0\fs24\b0\i0 : }{\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf6 "Yes, it is. I hope to top last year's record for this annual fundraising event."}
\par\plain {\f2\fs24\b1\i0\cf10 <$Scr_Cs::7>Evan: <!$Scr_Cs::7>}{\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf6 "Who else do I need to know about? The bartender said I may have to defend you against some salacious wolves?"}
\par\plain {\f3\fs24\b0\i1\cf9 <$Scr_Cs::6>[Evan humorously jumped into a boxer\loch\af3\hich\af3\dbch\af3\uc1\u8217\'92s pose with his dukes held high, causing Sarah to laugh. ]<!$Scr_Cs::6>}
\par\plain {\f2\fs24\b1\i0\cf10 <$Scr_Cs::7>Sarah: <!$Scr_Cs::7>}{\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf6 "Just having you by my side will spook them away. It will be nice not to have to deal with them for once."}
\par\plain {\f2\fs24\b1\i0\cf10 <$Scr_Cs::7>[ Sarah looked at her watch. ]}
\par\plain {\f2\fs24\b1\i0\cf10 Sarah: <!$Scr_Cs::7>}{\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf6 "We're out of time. Look, do your best. Don't be offended or surprised if a bunch of people try to get you to donate money. Since no one knows you, they may think you're a trust fund kid and see you as fresh meat."}
\par\plain {\f2\fs24\b1\i0\cf10 <$Scr_Cs::7>Evan:<!$Scr_Cs::7>}{\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf6  "Can I get a kiss before we head out into the den of wolves?"}
\par\plain {\f2\fs24\b1\i0\cf10 <$Scr_Cs::7>[ For reasons unknown to Evan but he finds amusing, he sees Sarah look left then right in a small room with a closed door. He thinks she's being a bit paranoid. ]}
\par\plain {\f2\fs24\b1\i0\cf10 Sarah:<!$Scr_Cs::7>}{\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf6  "Alight, one quick kiss, that's it."}
\par\plain {\f2\fs24\b1\i0\cf10 <$Scr_Cs::7>[ Sarah leaned in, and true to her word Evan got a quick kiss, and that was it. ]<!$Scr_Cs::7>}
\par\pard\plain \tx0\li720\fi-360\sb60\sl264\slmult1\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24\b1\i0\cf8 <$Scr_Ps::5>End: <!$Scr_Ps::5>}
\par\pard\plain \tx0\li720\sa120\sl264\slmult1\ltrch\loch {\f3\fs24\b0\i1\cf9 <$Scr_Cs::6>[ Sarah opened the door, peeked her head out, and looked both ways. With the coast clear, she and Evan walked down the hall toward The Grand Ballroom. ]}
\par\plain {\f3\fs24\b0\i1\cf9 [ As they reached the edge of the grand ballroom, illuminated by the soft glow of crystal chandeliers and filled with the murmur of elegant conversations, Evan turned to Sarah with an air of traditional gallantry. His eyes met hers, and with a slight, gentlemanly bow, he extended his arm toward her. Understanding the timeless gesture, Sarah gracefully slipped her arm into his, allowing her hand to rest just above his elbow. With arms interlocked, they ventured into the mystery of the evening ahead. ]<!$Scr_Cs::6>}
